typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		CampaignId as string,
		CampaignName as string,
		Creative as string,
		Date as string,
		Impressions as string,
		Clicks as string,
		ClickRate as string,
		TotalConversions as string,
		ClickThroughConversions as string,
		TfocoComDetailSubmitTotalConversions as string,
		NewTfocoComGlobalTagTotalConversions as string,
		NewTfocoComHomePageVisitTotalConversions as string,
		NewTfocoComInvestmentPlannerVisitTotalConversions as string,
		NewTfocoComPortfolioPlannerVisitTotalConversions as string,
		NewTfocoComWebinarSignupTotalConversions as string,
		NewTfocoComDetailSubmitTotalConversions as string,
		TfocoComHomePageVisitTotalConversions as string,
		TfocoComWealthPlanningTotalConversions as string,
		TfocoComWhoWeAreTotalConversions as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> GoogleDV360CampaignStage
GoogleDV360CampaignStage derive(Date = toDate(Date, 'yyyy-MM-dd')) ~> PrepareColumns
PrepareColumns sink(input(
		CampaignId as integer,
		CampaignName as string,
		Creative as string,
		Date as date,
		Impressions as double,
		Clicks as double,
		ClickRate as double,
		TotalConversions as double,
		ClickThroughConversions as double,
		TfocoComDetailSubmitTotalConversions as double,
		NewTfocoComGlobalTagTotalConversions as double,
		NewTfocoComHomePageVisitTotalConversions as double,
		NewTfocoComInvestmentPlannerVisitTotalConversions as double,
		NewTfocoComPortfolioPlannerVisitTotalConversions as double,
		NewTfocoComWebinarSignupTotalConversions as double,
		NewTfocoComDetailSubmitTotalConversions as double,
		TfocoComHomePageVisitTotalConversions as double,
		TfocoComWealthPlanningTotalConversions as double,
		TfocoComWhoWeAreTotalConversions as double
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	deletable:false,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:false,
	format: 'table',
	mapColumn(
		CampaignId,
		CampaignName,
		Creative,
		Date,
		Impressions,
		Clicks,
		ClickRate,
		TotalConversions,
		ClickThroughConversions,
		TfocoComDetailSubmitTotalConversions,
		NewTfocoComGlobalTagTotalConversions,
		NewTfocoComHomePageVisitTotalConversions,
		NewTfocoComInvestmentPlannerVisitTotalConversions,
		NewTfocoComPortfolioPlannerVisitTotalConversions,
		NewTfocoComWebinarSignupTotalConversions,
		NewTfocoComDetailSubmitTotalConversions,
		TfocoComHomePageVisitTotalConversions,
		TfocoComWealthPlanningTotalConversions,
		TfocoComWhoWeAreTotalConversions
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	errorHandlingOption: 'stopOnFirstError') ~> GoogleDV360Campaign
